LT3 LIABILITY TRADING – NON-NEGOTIABLE RULES

1. NO trading unless a tender has been accepted.
2. NO front-running or pre-hedging.
3. NO market making behavior.
4. Only unwind accepted tender inventory.
5. Prefer small losses over fines.
6. Always flatten before end of simulation.
7. Use immediate market or marketable-limit orders only.
8. VWAP and liquidity checks must be based on current book only.
9. Do not use OHLC, TAS, or historical prediction.
